-- 🕵️ ลูป Auto-Detector สแกนหาระยะพิกัดคนโกงย้อนหลังให้อัตโนมัติเบื้องหลังเงียบ ๆ ตลอดเวลา (รายชื่อเด้งชัวร์)
local lastPositions, lastTimes = {}, {}
task.spawn(function() while task.wait(0.7) do for _, p in pairs(Players:GetPlayers()) do if p ~= LocalPlayer and p.Character and p.Character:FindFirstChild("HumanoidRootPart") and p.Character:FindFirstChildOfClass("Humanoid") then local hrp = p.Character.HumanoidRootPart local currentPos, currentTime = hrp.Position, os.clock() if lastPositions[p] and lastTimes[p] then local dist = (Vector3.new(currentPos.X, 0, currentPos.Z) - Vector3.new(lastPositions[p].X, 0, lastPositions[p].Z)).Magnitude local dt = currentTime - lastTimes[p] local mathSpeed = dist / dt local vertDist = math.abs(currentPos.Y - lastPositions[p].Y) local verticalSpeed = vertDist / dt if mathSpeed > 45 and p.Character.Humanoid.WalkSpeed > 0 and _G.AddSuspectReportFunc then _G.AddSuspectReportFunc(p, "Speed ("..math.floor(mathSpeed)..")") end if verticalSpeed > 50 and p.Character.Humanoid:GetState() == Enum.HumanoidStateType.Freefall and _G.AddSuspectReportFunc then _G.AddSuspectReportFunc(p, "Fly / Teleport") end end lastPositions[p], lastTimes[p] = currentPos, currentTime end end if _G.SpectatingPlayer and not MainFrame.Visible then pcall(function() Camera.CameraSubject = LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChildOfClass("Humanoid") end) _G.SpectatingPlayer = nil end end end)
